"AP699E9N.BT1738-4-DL" and "REV1.0" ''appears'' to :be silkscreened on the board in the [https://fccid.io/document.php?id=2041039 FCC photos]. [https://fccid.io/document.php?id=2041042 FCC docs] state that this FCC ID: [https://fccid.io/KA2IR300D1 KA2IR300D1] also covers: *[[D-Link DIR-600]] ([[D-Link DIR-600L rev B1]]) *[[D-Link DIR-607]]
===Serial=== The serial port on board marked "J1". Levels is TTL 3.3V. :Pins: 1 - VCC, 2 - GND, 3 and 4 - Data (Rx and Tx).
Baud rate: 38400 Data bits: 8 Parity: none Stop bits: 1
